<p source="SHANGBO.JUNRENZHE 7.41.1 (STRIPS 1-2) MACHENGYUAN 7: 193, 197 TR. MARCO CABOARA">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0070_tls_001-1a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0070_tls_001-1a.1">范戊曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0070_tls_001-1a.2">“君王有白玉三回</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0070_tls_001-1a.3">而不戔[殘],</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0070_tls_001-1a.4">命爲君王戔[殘]之,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0070_tls_001-1a.5">敢告於視日.”</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0070_tls_001-1a.6">王乃出而【1】見之.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0070_tls_001-1a.7">王曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0070_tls_001-1a.8">“范乘,吾焉有白玉三回</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0070_tls_001-1a.9">而不戔[殘]哉?”</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.JUNRENZHE 7.41.2 (STRIPS 2-3) MACHENGYUAN 7: 197-198 TR. MARCO CABOARA">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0070_tls_001-2a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0070_tls_001-2a.1">范乘曰:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0070_tls_001-2a.2">“楚邦之中有食【2】田五畛,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0070_tls_001-2a.3">竽管衡於前.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0070_tls_001-2a.4">君王有楚,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0070_tls_001-2a.5">不聽鼓鐘之聲,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0070_tls_001-2a.6">此 其一回[違]也.</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.JUNRENZHE 7.41.3 (STRIPS 3-4) MACHENGYUAN 7: 198, 200 TR. MARCO CABOARA">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0070_tls_001-3a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0070_tls_001-3a.1">珪玉之君,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0070_tls_001-3a.2">百【3】畛之主,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0070_tls_001-3a.3">宮妾以十百數.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0070_tls_001-3a.4">君王有楚,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0070_tls_001-3a.5">侯子三人,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0070_tls_001-3a.6">一人杜門而不出,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0070_tls_001-3a.7">此其二回也.</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.JUNRENZHE 7.41.4 (STRIPS 4-6) MACHENGYUAN 7: 200, 202, 203 TR. MARCO CABOARA">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0070_tls_001-4a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0070_tls_001-4a.1">州徒(?)【4】之樂,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0070_tls_001-4a.2">而天下莫不禦,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0070_tls_001-4a.3">先王之所以爲目觀也.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0070_tls_001-4a.4">君王隆[恭]其祭</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0070_tls_001-4a.5">而不爲 其樂,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0070_tls_001-4a.6">[六]【5】此其三回也.</seg>
                </p>

<p source="SHANGBO.JUNRENZHE 7.41.5 (STRIPS 6-8) MACHENGYUAN 7: 203-205 TR. MARCO CABOARA">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0070_tls_001-5a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0070_tls_001-5a.1">先王爲此,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0070_tls_001-5a.2">人謂之安邦,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0070_tls_001-5a.3">謂之利民.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0070_tls_001-5a.4">今君王盡去耳【6】目之欲,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0070_tls_001-5a.5">人以君王為所[疏] 以敖.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0070_tls_001-5a.6">民有不能也,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0070_tls_001-5a.7">鬼無不能也,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0070_tls_001-5a.8">民詛而使應【7】之,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0070_tls_001-5a.9">君王雖[唯]不長年,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0070_tls_001-5a.10">可也.</seg>
                </p>

